# Frontend env (Vite reads this at build/dev time).
# `npx convex dev` writes the real value of VITE_CONVEX_URL into .env.local —
# do not put it here.
#
# Secrets DO NOT belong in any .env* file in this repo. GEMINI_API_KEY in
# particular must be set on the Convex deployment:
#   npx convex env set GEMINI_API_KEY <your-key>
# That keeps it server-side only — out of the browser bundle.
